The program \fBgwbasic\fP written by Christian A. Ratliff
was a detokenizer for GW-Basic, the IBM-PC Basic interpreter. The
present program is inspired by it, but given the much simpler
structure of tokenized Basic on the Thomson it is written as a very
simple Unix filter. 
.\"}}}
